<div class="home-main">
<h1>Welcome to P J Hayman &amp; Company Limited</h1>
<p><img class="stamp" src="images/stamp.jpg" alt="" />P J Hayman &amp; Company (PJH) is a specialist Travel Insurance and Schemes provider founded in 1990.</p>
<p>Over the years, PJH has built a reputation as a well-respected Travel Insurance and schemes intermediary. We work very closely with insurance underwriters and service providers to ensure that our clients, be they individuals, brokers, affinity groups, scheme providers, direct sellers or the travel trade, receive a product that best suits their needs.</p>
<p><a href="/about/" onclick="__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'download', '/about/');" class="text-link">READ MORE </a><span class="text-arrow"><a href="/about/" onclick="__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'download', '/about/');" class="text-link">»<br />
</a></span></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3104" src="http://www.pjhayman.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/lloyds-large-300x53-300x53.jpg" alt="PJ Hayman are coverholders at Lloyds" width="300" height="53" srcset="http://www.pjhayman.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/lloyds-large-300x53.jpg 300w, http://www.pjhayman.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/lloyds-large-300x53-220x39.jpg 220w, http://www.pjhayman.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/lloyds-large-300x53-187x33.jpg 187w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
</div>
<div class="home-large-panels-1">
<h2>TRAVEL INSURANCE</h2>
<p>With over 25 years experience in travel insurance, we have created specific products to cater for specific needs. Whether you require cover for a medical condition, hazardous activities, round the world trip, Gap year, etc., we have a policy for you.</p>
<div class="click-panel"><a href="http://www.pjhayman.com/travel-insurance/">MORE INFORMATION <span class="text-arrow">»</span></a></div>
</div>
<div class="home-large-panels-2">
<h2>PERSONAL INSURANCE</h2>
<p>As schemes specialists, we are able to provide some unique products; these currently include: ‘Top-up’ Cancellation cover; Euro Plus (breakdown cover for people travelling to Europe); and PJH Worldwide for those who have already travelled and expats.</p>
<div class="click-panel"><a href="http://www.pjhayman.com/personal-insurance/">MORE INFORMATION <span class="text-arrow">»</span></a></div>
</div>
<div class="home-large-panels-3">
<h2>CORPORATE INSURANCE</h2>
<p>We have a range of facilities to cover companies; ranging from Group Personal Accident and Travel to Liability cover for Tour Operators. Specific products include: Business; Coach Plus Breakdown; Coach Plus Driver; Cyber Risks Cover; SAFI and IIA Travel Protector.</p>
<div class="click-panel"><a href="http://www.pjhayman.com/corporate-insurance/">MORE INFORMATION <span class="text-arrow">»</span></a></div>
</div>
<div class="clear"></div>
<div class="more-info">MORE INFORMATION</div>
<div class="home-small-panels-1">
<h4>NO AGE LIMIT</h4>
<p>Our Free Spirit policy is one of the few available in the travel insurance market not to have an upper age limit.</p>
<div class="click-panel2"><a href="/travel-insurance/free-spirit/">READ MORE <span class="text-arrow">»</span></a></div>
</div>
<div class="home-small-panels-2">
<h4>ALREADY TRAVELLED?</h4>
<p>Cover available for UK Nationals already abroad, Expatriates and other Nationals. Short or long term policies available.</p>
<div class="click-panel2"><a href="/travel-insurance/worldwide-already-travelled/">READ MORE <span class="text-arrow">»</span></a></div>
</div>
<div class="home-small-panels-2">
<h4>OPEN AN ACCOUNT</h4>
<p>For Brokers and Agents who wish to open an account with us, please click below and follow the simple steps.</p>
<div class="click-panel2"><a href="https://www.pjhaymanb2b.com/open-an-account" target="_blank" rel="noopener">OPEN ACCOUNT <span class="text-arrow">»</span></a></div>
